fdncred 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10113] bumped rust-toolchain to 1.70.0
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10101] bumped nushell to dev version 0.84.1
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10091] removeed 
``--column``
 from 
``length``
 command and remove 
``record``
 processing
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10086] updated install/build scripts to include 
``--locked``
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10082] allowed 
``help``
 to return a 
``Type::Table``
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10067] allowed 
``return``
 to return any nushell value
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10063] tried to fix 
``into datetime``
 to accept more dt formats
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10058] enabled/updated some example tests so they work again
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10057] tried to document the more obscure testbin commands
